        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>(SN) In nomine domini Dei eterni. Ani a. incarnacione domini nostri Iesu
                        Christi millesimo centesimo viesimo octavo, quinto die mensis ienuarius,
                        indicione sexta. Constat nos <persName
                            key="#childOf #parentOf #parentInLawOf #Lombard #Offersio/donatio"><name
                                ref="Azo">Azo</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#childOf">filius</rs> quondam <persName key="#parentOf #Lombard"
                                ><name ref="Azo">Azonis</name></persName> et <persName
                            key="#marriage #Lombard #Offersio/donatio"><name ref="Ardoinus"
                                >Ardoinus</name></persName> et <persName
                            key="#marriage #childOf #childInLawOf #Lombard #parentOf #Offersio/donatio"
                                ><name ref="Alda">Alda</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#marriage">iugalibus</rs>, filia quondam <persName
                            key="#parentOf #Lombard"><name ref="Ingo">Ingo</name></persName> de
                            <placeName ref="#places/4114">Negraro</placeName>, et <persName
                            key="#marriage #Lombard #Offersio/donatio"><name ref="Taruso"
                                >Taruso</name></persName> et <persName
                            key="#marriage #childOf #childInLawOf #Lombard #Offersio/donatio"><name
                                ref="Cliemaro">Cliemaro</name></persName> filia <persName
                            key="#parentOf #Lombard #Witness"><name ref="Heinricus"
                            >Enricus</name></persName> de <placeName ref="#places/577"
                            >Pruno</placeName>, filiis et <rs key="#childInLawOf">nuris</rs>
                        suprasctipto Azo, abitaturis in <geogName key="#Iudiciaria"
                            ref="#estates/2076"><rs key="#Iudiciaria">iudicaria</rs>
                            Gardense</geogName>, infra <rs key="#Castle">castro</rs>
                        <placeName key="#Castle" ref="#places/4115">Pesena</placeName>, qui profesi
                        summus ex nacione nostra lege vivere <rs key="#Lombard">Lagobardorum</rs>,
                        ipsis namque iugalibus nostris nobis consencientibus et subter conrirmante,
                        una cum noticia de propiquioribus <rs key="#kinOf">parentibus</rs> nostris
                        nobis consencientibus et subter confirmante, i sunt: <persName
                            key="#kinOf #Witness"><name ref="Ermenaldus">Ermenardo</name></persName>
                        de <placeName ref="#places/4116">Vualgatara</placeName> et <persName
                            key="#childOf #Witness"><name ref="Trufaldus">Trufaldo</name></persName>
                        filius suprascripta Alda et suprascripto Enricus pater suprascripta
                        Cliemaro, in corum presentia vel <rs key="#Witness">testium</rs> certa
                        facimus profesione quod nullum patimus viollenciam nec ab ipsis iugalibus
                        nostris, <rs key="#Offersio/donatio">cartam donacionis et ofersionis</rs>
                        nomine de suorum manibus in manu de <persName
                            key="#Monks #Missus #Monasteries"><name ref="Symeon"
                            >Simeon</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Monks">monahus</rs> et <rs key="#Missus">misus</rs>
                        <rs key="#Monasteries">monasterii</rs>
                        <orgName key="#Monasteries #Monks #Missus" ref="#juridical_persons/2001"
                            >Sancti Benedicti a Laeruno</orgName>, pro anima nostra seu et
                        parentorum nostrorum mercede, id est <rs
                            key="#Mansi #Casae/cassinae_massaricie">masaricia una</rs> quod est <rs
                            key="#Agricultural_workers">laborata</rs> per <persName
                            key="#Agricultural_workers"><name ref="Martinus"
                            >Martino</name></persName>, tam <rs key="#Landed_possessions">tera</rs>
                        cum <rs key="#Houses">casa paladicia</rs> et terris cum <rs key="#Wine"
                            >vineis</rs> et <rs key="#Cereals">terris aratoreis</rs> et <rs
                            key="#Hay/fodder">terris pradivis</rs>, et terris cum <rs key="#Forests"
                            >silvis</rs>; et duas <rs key="#Petiae">pecias</rs> de terris aratoreis
                        quod iacet in campagna de <placeName key="#Petiae #Cereals"
                            ref="#places/4117">Castelloni</placeName>, et terra que tenet <persName
                            key="#childOf"><name ref="Otto">Oto</name></persName> filius quondam
                            <persName key="#parentOf"><name ref="Rodulfus"
                        >Rodulfo</name></persName>*** de <placeName ref="#places/1822"
                            >Pesscera</placeName>, qui posite sunt in iudicaria Gardense, locus ubi
                        dicitur <placeName ref="#places/4118">Tavernolle</placeName>, et omnes ius
                        de <rs key="#Common_land">comunia</rs> quod eorum pertinet in eodem loco
                        Tavernolle. Et insuper dederunt suprascripto Azo et filiis et nuris omnia
                        quod abent in <placeName ref="#places/4119">Plovezano</placeName>, i sunt
                        noves pecias de terris. Prima pecia de terra aratoria, quod iacet prope
                        castro locus ubi dicitur <placeName key="#Petiae #Cereals #Castle #Roads"
                            >Flabiolo</placeName>, abent <rs key="#Size">per longum de ambobus
                            lateribus perticas treginta et duas et pedes sex; de uno capite perticas
                            trex pedes sex, de allio capite perticas duas</rs>; de uno latere iura
                            <orgName ref="#juridical_persons/90">Sancti Zenonis</orgName> posident,
                        de allio latere et ambobus capitibus <rs key="#Roads">via percurente</rs>.
                        Secunda pecia de terra aratoria, quod iacet in loco qui dicitur <placeName
                            key="#Petiae #Cereals">Allavuallo</placeName>, abent <rs key="#Size">per
                            longum perticas decem et novem et pedes sex; de uno capite pertica una
                            et pedes octo, de allio perticas trex et pedes trex, et de allio latus
                            perticas novem, de allia parte perticas quinque, de allio perticas
                            quaptuor</rs>, de uno latere <persName><name ref="Vivianus/Biviaqua"
                                >Viviano Biviaqua</name></persName> de <placeName ref="#places/59"
                            >Verona</placeName> abente, de allio latere <persName><name
                                ref="Crescentius">Cresenzo</name></persName> presbiter abente, de
                        uno capite <persName><name ref="Iohannes">Iohannes</name></persName>, de
                        allio <persName><name ref="Albertus">Alberto</name></persName>, de alio via
                        percurente. Tercia ibi prope abent <rs key="#Size">per longum de ambobus
                            lateribus perticas viginti et septem; de uno capite perticas duas pedes
                            duos, de allio capite pertica una pedes sex</rs>; de uno latere et uno
                        capite suprascripto Viviano abent, de allio latere iura Sancti Zenonis, de
                        allio comunia adest. Pecia quarta ubi dicitur a <placeName key="#Petiae"
                            >Campara</placeName>, <rs key="#Size">de ambobus lateribus quadraginta
                            et octo; de uno capite perticas septem, de allio perticas sex</rs>; de
                        ambobus capitibus via. Quinta pecia de terra locus ubi dicitur <placeName
                            key="#Petiae">Paullo</placeName>
                        <rs key="#Size">de ambobus lateribus perticas viginti et una et pedes sex;
                            de uno capite pertica una, pedes sex, de allio pertica una pedes
                            decem;</rs> de uno latere <orgName ref="#juridical_persons/2461">Sancta
                            Maria</orgName> de <placeName ref="#places/2943">Cissano</placeName>, de
                        allio latere <orgName>Sancto Zulliano</orgName>, de uno capite via, de allio
                                <persName><name ref="Bertram/de Arzei">Bertram</name></persName> de
                            <placeName ref="#places/4122">Arzei</placeName>. Sexsta terra pradiva
                        locus ubi dicitur a <placeName key="#Petiae">Montellongo</placeName>, <rs
                            key="#Size">per longum de ambobus lateribus perticas viginti et octo
                            pedes trex; de uno capite pertica una pede uno, de allio perticas
                            quaptuor</rs>; de uno latere <persName><name ref="Maurus"
                            >Mauro</name></persName> de <placeName ref="#places/4120"
                            >Pastrego</placeName> abet, de alio <persName><name
                                ref="Zenus/de Verona">Zeno</name></persName> da Verona; de uno
                        capite comugna, de allio <persName><name ref="Petrus"
                            >Petro</name></persName> abet. Et duas pecias de terra, una aratoria et
                        allia pradiva, insimul tenente locus ubi dicitur <placeName
                            key="#Petiae #Cereals #Hay/fodder #Roads">Ario</placeName>; <rs
                            key="#Size">per longum perticas treginta et duas, de allio treginta et
                            septem; de ambobus capitibus perticas octo pedes sex</rs>; de uno latere
                        Sancto Zeno, de allio <persName><name ref="Martinus"
                            >Martino</name></persName> de <placeName ref="#places/4121"
                            >Calmasini</placeName> abent; de uno capite via, de alio <persName><name
                                ref="Cuneradus">Conrado</name></persName> abent. Et pecia de terra
                        pradiva locus ubi dicitur a <placeName key="#Petiae #Hay/fodder">Pra
                            Maioro</placeName>. Et allia pecia de terra busscareza prope castro; et
                        omne ius de comunia quod eorum pertinet, una cum accesionibus et ingresoras
                        earum rerum, sicut supra legitur, in integrum nos suprascripti Azo et filiis
                        et nuris et suorum eredibus ab omni omine defensare; quod si defendere non
                        potuerimus, tunc <rs key="#Penalty">in duplum</rs> restituamus ad
                        suprascripto monasterio. Actum in suprascripto castro Pesena. Fellciter.
                        Signum manibus suprascripti Azo et filiis et nuris, qui ac cartam fieri
                        rogavi ut supra legitur. Signum manibus <persName
                            key="#Witness #Offersio/donatio"><name ref="Gherardus"
                            >Girardo</name></persName>, <persName key="#Witness #Offersio/donatio"
                                ><name ref="Lanzus">Lanzo</name></persName>, <persName
                            key="#Witness #Offersio/donatio"><name ref="Maraldus"
                            >Maraldo</name></persName>, <persName key="#Witness #Offersio/donatio"
                                ><name ref="Francus">Franco</name></persName>, <persName
                            key="#Witness #Offersio/donatio"><name ref="Inibertus"
                            >Iniberto</name></persName> de Pesena, <persName
                            key="#Witness #Offersio/donatio"><name ref="Ingelerius"
                            >Ingellero</name></persName>
                        <rs>legis doctu</rs> et <persName key="#Witness #Offersio/donatio"><name
                                ref="Hugo  ">Uho</name></persName> de Bardolino. (SN) Ego <persName
                            key="#Notary #Offersio/donatio"><name ref="Persenaldus"
                                >Persenaldus</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Notary">notarius</rs> rogatus qui ibi fui et post tradita
                        complevi. </ab>
                </div>
            </div>
